--Allentown has thirty gas street lights, and pays $3 per thousand feet;
                        Easton seventy-five lights, $3 per thousand feet; Pottsville, seventy-three
                        light, $3 30 per thousand feet; Reading, forty-three lights $2 87 per
                        thousand feet; Harrisburg, seventy-three lights, $2 50 per thousand feet;
                        Lancaster, one hundred lights, $3 per one thousand feet; Norristown,
                        seventy-three lights, $2 50 per thousand feet.
